2026-05-03T23:55:10.8232853Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8233668Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8234461Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8265558Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8266543Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8267410Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8268243Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-03T23:55:10.8269020Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
